data.description: ELEGANT CUSTOM HOME IN QUIET WATERFRONT NEIGHBORHOOD: This Zyta construction home built in 2000 is uniquely situated on two city lots adjoining waterfront forest land. This accessible single-level home offers open living-spaces, vaulted ceilings and high-quality finishes. There is ample room for your RV & hobbies in the detached shop & an exciting bonus space ready for your imagination. You can tell from the moment you open the double doors that every detail in this home has been considered.
